    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given the narrowly scoped COU limited to ASTM F1717 compression-bending. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96, MAPE < 10%) are satisfied for all three QoIs across N=11 specimens from two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context.",
